.  The gaze is down or forward.</p></li></ul><ul><li><h5>Benefits:</h5><p class='text'>Stretches the entire front of the body, ankles, thighs, groins, abdomen, chest, throat and deep hip flexors (psoas).  Strengthens the back muscles.  Improves posture.  Stimulates the organs of the abdomen and neck.</p></li></ul></section>        </section>

